data.description: Welcome to your stunning new home! This fabulous 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts an open floor plan concept, provides the master suite separate, from other bedrooms. The Kitchen features plenty of large 42" cabinets, with a breakfast bar, that makes a perfect space for hosting events and gatherings with loved ones. Oversized Walkin pantry and includes a reverse osmosis system. This home has everything you need inside and out, wood blinds, ceiling fans throughout, a water softener, 2 car garage with insulated walls, beautiful back yard with a 10x10 waterproof floored storage shed, also includes patio area for a fire pit. The home is located in a small subdivision with easy access to IH-35, and shopping. Assumable loan at 2.99%, come out and take a look today.
